    <item>
      <title>尽管销售增长放缓，博通首席执行官仍预计人工智能将带来意外收获</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/broadcom-grows-at-slowest-pace-since-2020-in-face-of-chip-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司和其他大型科技公司的芯片供应商博通公司预计，人工智能计算的快速扩张将有助于抵消 2020 年以来最严重的经济放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/broadcom-grows-at-slowest-pace-since-2020-in-face-of-chip-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 21:34:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Spotify 首席财务官即将离职，营销主管也随之离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/spotify-is-losing-top-marketing-exec-cutting-podcasts-amid-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Spotify Technology SA 表示，首席财务官保罗·沃格尔 (Paul Vogel) 即将离职，这标志着这家音乐流媒体领军企业继本周宣布大幅裁员之后，再次出现高层离职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/spotify-is-losing-top-marketing-exec-cutting-podcasts-amid-restructuring</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 20:04:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
